latestIgtvVideos.title: QUARANTINE FACE GROOMING🪒✂️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We’re in a lockdown our facial hair isn’t. I was gonna groom my face and thought, hmm, why not film a video! This one is just to show you how you can groom your face in this lockdown and even generally. 
I used to bleach my face hair, but one day last year I just decided to try shaving the hair off and I was SO HAPPY that I did! The hair does not become hard or thick after shaving, the growth reduces, and I get this flawless canvas for my makeup! I don’t depend on anyone else for this. I have been using an epilator/trimmer for my brows and upper lip for years.
You can definitely try this out, just be careful while doing it. It’s completely safe and painfree! .

Nam Doyun >>> 🫶🏻😭🌸🌳💕

It’s the little things & gestures 🤌🏻.. I cried so much while reading this chapter 🥹 ISTG this Webtoon is so beautiful & so much fun! There’s not a single part that I didn’t like 🙌🏻

Reel Context:
Doyun fell first, but Jieon confessed first, and now Doyun had been trying to confess as well, so he asked his manager for advice, who told him about giving flowers while confessing - the bigger the better - and the manager (not knowing the girl in question) also told Jieon about it. Now Jieon was excited & expecting a confession with flowers from Doyun all day long but nothing happened. Then she heard him confess in his drama shoot (he’s an actor) which she concluded was how she’d end up hearing his confession and the advice he asked was for the drama scene, and got sad. But then at the end of the day he took her to show the first cherry blossoms of the season which was also “the biggest bouquet of flowers” from him to her and he finally confessed, WHICH was OFCOURSE totally different from his dramas, infact EVEN BETTER THAN DRAMAS, and was a side of him only she could see 💗🥹🌸😭
